    <div class="text-block shared-styles js-add-wrapper" data-wrap="table" data-wrap-class="table-scroll" data-aos-once="true" data-aos="fade-up">
        <p class="text--h6 char-overline">Skalitz</p>
<h3 class="text--h3">Henry</h3>
<p>A blacksmith's son who lost his parents when Sigismund's forces raided his home village of Skalitz. Henry becomes a key member of the resistance and he embarks on a journey motivated by revenge and a desire for adventure (and his love of a good stew). Thrown into the chaos of war, Henry must now choose between doing what's right and what's necessary to stop the invading forces and protect his friends. </p>
    </div>

