        <p class="text--h6 char-overline">Rattay</p>
<h3 class="text--h3">Hans</h3>
<p>Hans is a young Bohemian nobleman and Henry's friend from the previous game. He is known for his pompous yet lively and carefree personality, as well as his exceptional archery skills. Hans is based on a real historical figure of the same name, a hereditary lord of the town of Rattay. After the death of his parents, the Lords of Leipa became his guardians.  </p>
    </div>

