    <div class="text-block shared-styles js-add-wrapper" data-wrap="table" data-wrap-class="table-scroll" data-aos-once="true" data-aos="fade-up">
        <p class="text--h6 char-overline">Prague</p>
<h3 class="text--h3">Markvart</h3>
<p>Markvart, a central villain in the previous title, was responsible for the death of Henry's parents during the raid on Skalitz. Based on a real historical figure of the same name, he was a German noble. As the leader of the Cuman and Prague armies serving Sigismund, he plays a pivotal role in advancing Sigismund's conquest.</p>
